data.description: Welcome to 410 Cedar Creek Rd nestled on 7.22 acres of pure tranquility! This warm and inviting 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is a haven of comfort, offering a perfect blend of rustic charm and modern amenities. As you approach the rocking chair front porch on the stone walkway, it sets the tone for what's inside. Cozy living room featuring hardwood floors, brick fireplace and breathtaking views of nature from the attached screened-in back porch, Custom Eat-in Kitchen with built-ins, pendant lighting, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, double ovens, bay window and massive bar perfect for baking cookies with the children, separate formal dining space. Owners suite with double vanity, soaking tub and walk-in closet as well as laundry room with plenty of storage located on the main, 2 additional bedrooms up with shared full bath,  2 car attached garage. Unwind and appreciate the beauty of the outdoors. Entertaining is a breeze with ample space for family gatherings. Keep 4-legged and 2-legged babies safe and sound in the fenced in back yard. Whether it's the firepit under the stars or the detached screened-in porch, there's a spot for every occasion. Detached workshop/ garage/ office with electricity provides a perfect space for hobbies and projects.  Storage space is plentiful, ensuring a clutter-free environment. This farmhouse isn't just a home, it's a retreat. Brooks | Madras | Northgate School District, Minutes from I-85, Call your agent to view today!
